{"tid":2275692,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★突發！美國駐港領事館突撤離600名員工","createTime":"2020-11-07T10:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T11:15:42.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"636a8af99026366b0bf0c3457db46b169d73bf1e","tid":2275692,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5632054/org/ffe34ab8cda7192c7160086543d67f0c.jpg/5vhsJqOJ8tlMM6GQOjQNHyltyJUoPBzwtaE907WhPdM?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5632054%2Forg%2Fffe34ab8cda7192c7160086543d67f0c.jpg%2F5vhsJqOJ8tlMM6GQOjQNHyltyJUoPBzwtaE907WhPdM%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=966f6044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼早前放售南區壽山村道六幢超級洋房後，美國駐港澳總領事館再有異動。《香港01》獲悉，美國駐港領事館計劃進行大規模裝修，需暫時搬遷至另一地方運作，涉及約600名職員，惟至今未覓得發展商或業主出租辦公室。<br />\n<br />\n美國駐港總領事館回應查詢時承認，美國政府計劃翻新及優化美方在香港之物業，包括駐港總領事館，當中翻新工程需要暫時安置部分職員至其他地方，美國駐外使領館運作局（Bureau of Overseas Buildings Operations）會物色可供出租、符合運作需要的替代地方。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指，物色新地方過程正在進行中，目前只屬初步階段（very early stages），不評論選址、洽租發展商或業主、談判細節等資料。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/545134/01%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E7%BE%8E%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%A8%E6%93%AC%E7%BF%BB%E6%96%B0-%E8%A6%93%E6%A8%93%E9%9D%A2%E6%90%AC%E9%81%B7%E9%81%87%E9%98%BB%E6%BB%AF-%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%A8-%E5%B1%AC%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F545134%2F01%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%25A7%2590%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E6%2593%25AC%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E8%25A6%2593%25E6%25A8%2593%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%2590%25AC%25E9%2581%25B7%25E9%2581%2587%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%25BB%25AF-%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%2588%259D%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E9%259A%258E%25E6%25AE%25B5&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=f96edcd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/545134/01%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E7%BE%8E%E9%A7%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%A8%E6%93%AC%E7%BF%BB%E6%96%B0-%E8%A6%93%E6%A8%93%E9%9D%A2%E6%90%AC%E9%81%B7%E9%81%87%E9%98%BB%E6%BB%AF-%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%A8-%E5%B1%AC%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5</a>"},{"pid":"b9d806698e008235b9860fbcb4ca778af0d79da4","tid":2275692,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0adf04619bcd16042e4cd5af2844001cae05da","tid":2275692,"uid":1149,"like":13,"dislike":7,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"你老母標题黨"},{"pid":"e2d3645cc919fa740e655233ade7e781dca9e099","tid":2275692,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"美國駐港領事館計劃進行大規模裝修<br />\nFCed<br />\n唔好乜野都賴落政治度 上綱上線 過分解讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fcd8d32e913e1a85687cb0c55d6fd87adf5f9f","tid":2275692,"uid":103262,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:42:16.000Z","msg":"又借啲意post 支那01<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25936b5f99f9a5319d7b3b5ca4928d42799c5e81","tid":2275692,"uid":47857,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2d0adf04619bcd16042e4cd5af2844001cae05da","tid":2275692,"uid":1149,"like":13,"dislike":7,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"你老母標题黨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:42:27.00